Invocation Name: simpson's quote finder
des: The Simpson's Quote Finder will take any quote you can kind-of/sort-of remember from the show The Simpson's and find the episode it belongs to. This Skill makes use of SimpsonQuotes.com's search API but is in no way affiliated with FX Networks LLC who owns the rights to The Simpson's.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
